The '''2014 Düsseldorf Open''' was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Clay courts|clay courts]]. It was the second edition of the [[Düsseldorf Open (ATP Tour)|Düsseldorf Open]] as an [[ATP World Tour 250 series]] event on the [[2014 ATP World Tour]]. It took place at the [[Rochusclub]] in [[Düsseldorf]], [[Germany]], from May 18 through May 24, 2014.

